##  Sweet to meet you !

I'm Alice, the French illustrator behind My Sweet Paper Card, the joyful
stationery shop.

Our Sweet Cards & Stationery Gifts have unique designs that will spread joy
around you while also being sweet to the Planet : our cheerful products are
created using sustainable materials !

Learn more !
